com.fujitsu.xml.xlink.dataset
Interface ArcHashtable

public interface ArcHashtable

Interface that provides an arc information list table.
Arc information lists are mapped with a key character string.

Method Detail

get

public ArcList get(java.lang.String key)
The arc information list mapped with a specified key is obtained.
Valid arc information lists can be obtained with keys with the arc type element from attribute.
Parameters:
key - Key.
Returns:
The arc information list mapped with the key is returned.
If no arc information list is mapped or a null key is specified, null is returned.

size

public int size()
The number of registered keys is obtained.
Returns:
The number of registered keys is returned.

containsKey

public boolean containsKey(java.lang.String key)
Whether an arc information list is registered with the specified key is judged.
Parameters:
key - Key.
Returns:
The judgment result is returned.
true is returned when an arc information list is registered with the specified key; otherwise, false is returned.

keys

public java.util.Enumeration keys()
The list of registered keys is obtained.
Keys can be fetched sequentially by using the Enumeration method.
Returns:
The list of registered keys is returned.

elements

public java.util.Enumeration elements()
The list of registered arc information lists is obtained.
Arc information lists can be fetched sequentially by using the Enumeration method.
Returns:
The list of registered arc information lists is returned.
